explanation.summary: Kt qu in tm  cho thy nhp tim ca bn nhanh hn mc bnh thng, nhng cc tn hiu in tim vn n nh.
explanation.details: Hnh nh sng in tim cho thy nhp tim u n nhng p nhanh hn bnh thng. C th, nhp tim ca bn l 103.17 ln/pht, cao hn mc chun (60-100 ln/pht). Cc sng QRS (phn nhn cao) trn in tm  u hp, vi thi gian dn truyn in tim l 0.058s (58ms). Theo hng dn y khoa LITFL, cc sng QRS hp (<100ms) cho thy tn hiu in bt ngun t pha trn tm tht v ng dn truyn in ca tim hot ng bnh thng, khng c du hiu tc nghn. Ch s bin thin nhp tim (HRV) l 5.439ms thp, iu ny c th phn nh s cng thng hoc nhp tim t thay i.
explanation.recommendations: Bn nn ngh ngi, th gin v trnh cc cht kch thch nh c ph, tr, thuc l. Theo di c th  xem c cc triu chng nh hi hp, kh th hay khng.
explanation.next_steps: Nu nhp tim vn duy tr  mc cao khi bn  ngh ngi hon ton hoc xut hin cc triu chng kh chu, hy tham kho  kin bc s  c kim tra k hn.
